sources.description:
The Gatehouse | Full Movie | Mystery Adventure Movie | Award Winning Movie

10-Year-Old Eternity lives in a gatehouse at the edge of a forest and likes to dig for buried treasure. One day she digs up something she shouldn't, and the forest wants it back. What follows is a battle with an ancient force from a forgotten world.

2016.  Stars: Scarlett Rayner, Simeon Willis, Linal Haft
